      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POWER VALLEY (7) had been in great form but was out of the placings last run, finishing seventh (20.45) in a Grade 4 at this track. Normally fast to begin but shuffled back last time. Has a good record here at this journey. Looks the one to beat on his best form. VERMENTINO (5) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Was in the money last time (20.21) over 350m at this track in a Grade 5. Has never been out of the money in three starts this course and distance. Leading chance. INTEGRITY AL (1) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from six starts. Below best last time at this track (20.50) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5.5 lengths fifth. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. SATIN SPARKLE (6) won in smart time most recently. Right in the mix.",
